1	/**
2	 * Collection Report V2 — Sessions API
3	 *
4	 * GET  /api/collection-reports-v2/sessions  — List all sessions (grouped by sessionId)
5	 * POST /api/collection-reports-v2/sessions  — Start a new capture session for a location
6	 *
